            "title": "Transmit utilization in % per IFM uplink port",
            "showProgressBar": true,
            "description": "This panel shows the transmit utilization percentage for each IFM uplink port (iom_uplink role), based on the network_bandwidth_utilization_transmit metric. It helps monitor uplink performance from IO Modules, highlighting heavily utilized ports and aiding in bandwidth planning and congestion analysis."
        },
